## 🔑 API Details

| Item | Value |
|---|---|
| Provider | [OpenWeatherMap](https://openweathermap.org/api/air-pollution) |
| Endpoint | `https://api.openweathermap.org/data/2.5/air_pollution` |
| Geocoding | `https://api.openweathermap.org/geo/1.0/direct` |
| Key used | `b871b4234c3395d1b1321ebf4148e3c7` |
| Rate limit | 60 calls/minute on free plan |

