## 🎨 AQI Color Legend

| AQI Level | Label | Color | Action |
|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | Good | 🟢 Green | Outdoor activities safe |
| 2 | Fair | 🟡 Yellow | Sensitive groups be aware |
| 3 | Moderate | 🟠 Orange | Wear mask, reduce exertion |
| 4 | Poor | 🔴 Red | Avoid outdoor exercise |
| 5 | Very Poor | 🟣 Purple | Stay indoors |

