## 🛠️ Built With

- **HTML5 / CSS3 / Vanilla JS** — Zero build tools needed
- **[OpenWeatherMap API](https://openweathermap.org/)** — AQI + geocoding data
- **[Chart.js](https://www.chartjs.org/)** — AQI history line chart
- **[Leaflet.js](https://leafletjs.com/)** — Interactive pollution map
- **[CartoDB Dark Tiles](https://carto.com/)** — Dark-themed base map
- **[Google Fonts](https://fonts.google.com/)** — Syne + DM Sans typography

